---
---

<section id="testimonials" class="py-20 px-[6%] bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
  <div class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-3" data-i18n="testimonials.label">
        Cosa dicono i clienti
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4" data-i18n="testimonials.headline">
        Risultati reali, clienti soddisfatti
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 flex flex-col gap-4" data-animate>
        <div class="flex gap-1" aria-label="5 stelle su 5">
          {Array.from({length: 5}).map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
            </svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 leading-relaxed flex-grow" data-i18n="testimonials.items.1.quote">
          "Marco ha trasformato il nostro sito in qualcosa di cui siamo davvero orgogliosi. Il processo è stato semplice e il risultato supera le aspettative."
        </blockquote>
        <footer>
          <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="testimonials.items.1.name">Luca Bernasconi</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400" data-i18n="testimonials.items.1.role">Titolare, Bernasconi Impianti — Lugano</div>
        </footer>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 flex flex-col gap-4" data-animate>
        <div class="flex gap-1" aria-label="5 stelle su 5">
          {Array.from({length: 5}).map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
            </svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 leading-relaxed flex-grow" data-i18n="testimonials.items.2.quote">
          "L'automazione che Marco ha implementato ci fa risparmiare almeno 3 ore al giorno. Ogni settimana. Vale ogni centesimo."
        </blockquote>
        <footer>
          <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="testimonials.items.2.name">Sofia Mauri</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400" data-i18n="testimonials.items.2.role">Studio legale, Bellinzona</div>
        </footer>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 flex flex-col gap-4" data-animate>
        <div class="flex gap-1" aria-label="5 stelle su 5">
          {Array.from({length: 5}).map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
            </svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 leading-relaxed flex-grow" data-i18n="testimonials.items.3.quote">
          "Professionale, puntuale, e spiega tutto in modo comprensibile. Finalmente un tecnico con cui si può parlare senza dizionario."
        </blockquote>
        <footer>
          <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="testimonials.items.3.name">Roberto Fontana</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400" data-i18n="testimonials.items.3.role">Negozio di abbigliamento, Locarno</div>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
